      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E36 M3 delivers an authentic analog experience, powered by the S50 3.0L inline-six paired with a ZF 5-speed manual. The drivetrain is anchored by a 3.15 limited-slip differential, ensuring linear power delivery. Recent mechanical highlights include a cooling system refresh and a serviced VANOS unit. The chassis remains tight with upgraded bushings, offering the communicative steering feedback these cars are renowned for. While showing minor age-appropriate wear, this example is a mechanically robust driver's car with a healthy compression profile and a crisp shift action.",
