      "description": "Presenting a meticulously cared-for 2014 Luxury Sport Sedan that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily usability. This vehicle has been maintained with an open checkbook, and it shows in its current state. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might spot a minor stone chip on the lower front valence\u2014a testament to its enjoyed miles on the open road. Inside, the premium charcoal leather remains supple; there is only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, typical of careful use. All cabin electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium navigation system, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine pulls strongly and smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service history folder included with the sale. We recently completed a full synthetic oil service and a multi-point inspection, ensuring the vehicle is mechanically sound. The tires have roughly 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced just last season. This is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer looking for a reliable, high-end driving experience. Includes two sets of keys and all original owner's manuals.",
